    "description": "Pregnancy & Maternal Health Tracking and Risk Prediction\n\nSetup:\n1. Set base_url to https://nurtureher-proj.onrender.com/api\n2. Send the Login request — the token saves automatically\n3. All protected routes use Bearer token auth automatically",
